                    seating to encourage conversation, and ensure there's a clear flow of traffic.</p>
                </div>
  
                <div class="section-catalogue__faq-item">
                  <h5>How much space should there be between a sofa and a coffee table in a living room?</h5>
                  <p>Ideally, there should be about 18 inches of space between the sofa and the coffee table. This
                    distance allows for easy access and comfortable movement.</p>
                </div>
  
                <div class="section-catalogue__faq-item">
                  <h5>When decorating a living room, where do I start?</h5>
                  <p>Start by determining the room's focal point, such as a fireplace or large window. Arrange your
                    furniture around this focal point and choose a color scheme that complements it.</p>
                </div>
  
                <div class="section-catalogue__faq-item">
                  <h5>How do I choose living room colors?</h5>
